            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SURGT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Surrogate method was used to determine the",
                " fission cross section",
                "Surrogate reaction for 240Am(n,f) reaction was chosen",
                "243Am(p,t)241Am, which leads to the same compound",
                "nucleus 241Am. Surrogate for 235U(n,f) was reaction",
                "238U(p,t)236U. Surrogate ratio method was used with",
                "235U(n,f)as reference-monitor reaction."
              ]
            }
